    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Drinking glasses that have a complex, often twisting and intertwined, stem. The glasses may be flutes, goblets, wine glasses, or of many other forms.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
